            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1627379712957-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1627379712957-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once toasted, add 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>When the rice is boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Remove the rice from the heat and keep covered until serving – this is your <strong>nigella rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1627379719040-x200.jpg",
