            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into wedges</p>",
